section.section:
In selecting the members of the committee, the Governor shall solicit recommendations from each of the following:
Advisory Conference of Presidents;
Council on Postsecondary Education Student Advisory Committee;
Associations representing faculty from universities, technical institutions, and community colleges;
Associations representing university, technical institutions, and community college alumni;
Postsecondary education advocacy groups;
The Kentucky Board of Education;
Associations representing business and civic interests; and
Associations representing independent, nonprofit colleges and universities.
